{
  "stem": "214.4",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And she says, well, you will be going to the-- you will be working in the civilian hospital.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "You will be [GERMAN], domestic help.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And that's what it was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, I mean, as far as-- the only-- I remember, when I arrived there, they took me in.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They gave me some lunch.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they wanted to know about who I am, and what I am, and so forth and so on.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she said, would you like to take a bath.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Would I?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was worried.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, for some time, I was worried about the lice.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was so full of lice.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Under my arms, the whole body, everything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the conditions there, as far as working conditions-- so there I worked with three other Polish girls, and four Ukrainian girls.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we lived in the attic.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And all of them worked in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was only one-- I don't-- you know, it's really-- it's a matter of luck, I suppose.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And also, because the others were peasant girls, and I was sort of, you know, a city slicker.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I worked with another German girl, who was actually training to be a nurse, but they had to go through all those stages.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So she really-- she really taught me how to clean.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then she left, and another one came.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then, we worked in the hospital-- many times it was bombed out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then, but-- we-- I suppose most of the Poles felt that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But you really were not very much afraid of this bombing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You were hoping that it will bring the end of the war, though we were always the last ones.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That time, it was about 10 minutes past 2 o'clock in the morning.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
